⍝ lrm p. 37
      A←2 3 4
      ( 2(+)3     )  INV∆EQUIV  ( 2+3     )     ⍝ Primitive function name
      ( A+(.)×A   )  INV∆EQUIV  ( A+.×A   )     ⍝ Primitive operator name
      ( (2)+1     )  INV∆EQUIV  ( 2+1     )     ⍝ Primitive array name
      ( (A)←3     )  INV∆EQUIV  ( A←3     )     ⍝ Constructed array name
      ( ('ABC')   )  INV∆EQUIV  ( 'ABC'   )     ⍝ Character string
      ( ((2-3))+1 )  INV∆EQUIV (  (2-3)+1 )     ⍝ Parenthesized expression

      ( 2 (3) 4 )  INV∆EQUIV  ( 2 3 4 )    ⍝ These ( ) separate but do not group.
      ( (2 3 4) )  INV∆EQUIV  ( 2 3 4 )    ⍝ These group but do not separate.

